BUG-01: Form Submission with Empty Required Fields

Severity: High

Environment: Windows 11, Chrome Browser

Steps to Reproduce (STR):

1)Navigate to the "Sign-up & Profile Wizard."

2)Leave the "Full Name" and "Date of Birth" fields empty.

3)Fill in all other fields with valid data.

4)Click the "Next" button.

Expected Result: The form should not proceed. An error message should appear below the empty fields.

Actual Result: The form proceeds to the "Review" stage with empty values for name and dob.

Evidence:
  ![Screenshot showing the form submitted with an empty name and date of birth](evidence\bug-01-empty-fields.png)